{"tid":2022515,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"平社會：歧視支那人成香港社會現象 除咗發聲明無野可以做到","createTime":"2020-05-18T11:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T14:24:11.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"390c74536a7f922f46121033ccf677b0cf87a347","tid":2022515,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"平機會在立法會簡報過去一年的工作，平機會主席朱敏健表示，新型冠狀病毒疫情爆發以來，部分食肆拒絕招待內地人、或講普通話的顧客，這種歧視成為社會現象，而非針對個人的行為，平機會除了發強硬聲明之外，沒有其他工作可以做，期望可加強法律方面工作。<br />\n<br />\n朱敏健指出，反修例風波加上疫情，查詢及投訴比往年多，達到1526宗，當中部分投訴極具爭議性，除了歧視內地人，還有示威人士被指受到或作出性騷擾等，這些投訴令平機會的工作更困難，因為無論作出甚麼決定，都會受到不同意見的人士批評，平機會今年將會設立反性騷擾事務組，全面檢討現時與性騷擾相關的法例。"},{"pid":"e6b972bb9c7c60d817be8f84ce141c80761e5b16","tid":2022515,"uid":279981,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:21:14.000Z","msg":"告啦 仲唔告？ 告啦嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a0f8a9b6c196b135d4a5ba6f85aafca57bd7b4","tid":2022515,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6b972bb9c7c60d817be8f84ce141c80761e5b16","tid":2022515,"uid":279981,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:21:14.000Z","msg":"告啦 仲唔告？ 告啦嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:22:26.000Z","msg":"快D告<br />\n證明香港人唔係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3309c7c8ac2647c09748796d86cdb9f00a59bfd","tid":2022515,"uid":196719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"點解要分中國同香港人<br />\n香港咪係中國一部分<br />\n平機會違反一中原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b0a324dc0e71cac8a604305f3fe325193d8b32","tid"